page.title: Galactic Odyssey: Wang Ximing's Journey Through Space

revision.text:
[[zh:]] {{CC-BY-SA}}{{Infobox|image1=[[File:ChatGPT]]|Simplified Chinese=|English name=Galactic Odyssey: Wang Ximing's Journey Through Space|country={{China}}|genre=fiction (generated by ChatGPT)|production time=February 19, 2023|url=https://youtu.be/-OrrdPQQqxA}}'''''Galactic Odyssey: Wang Ximing's Journey Through Space''''' (Chinese name: '''''') is a science fiction novel generated by [[Wikipedia:ChatGPT|ChatGPT]]. The story follows [[Wang Ximing]], an astronaut who embarks on a space journey to explore the universe. The novel was generated on February 19, 2023, with a total of 3,812 words. ==Plot summary== Wang Ximing sets off on a space journey to explore the universe. During his journey, he encounters a series of breathtaking and mysterious sights, such as a nebula that appears like a giant dragon, and a planet with sentient life forms. Wang also meets an extraterrestrial race who shows him their advanced technology and takes him on a tour of their planet.
Despite the wonders he experiences, Wang Ximing still yearns for his wife and son back on Earth. The lack of communication with his loved ones causes him anxiety, but he finds solace in his interactions with the alien race, especially during moments of humor and shared interests.
After three days, Wang Ximing arrives at Kilvax, where he explores the planet and interacts with its inhabitants. He learns about their culture, and even falls in love with one of the natives. However, his stay is cut short when he is told that he must return to Earth due to an impending danger.
Upon his return to Earth, Wang Ximing finds that much time has passed and his loved ones have aged. He is haunted by the feeling of having lost time and missed out on the lives of his wife and son. Despite this, he is comforted by the knowledge that he has experienced things that no human has before, and the hope that he will one day be able to embark on another adventure. ==Ending== As Wang Ximing settles back into life on Earth, he receives a mysterious message from an unknown source, hinting at the possibility of another adventure. The novel ends with Wang Ximing gazing up at the night sky, his heart filled with a sense of longing and wonder. ==Reception== The novel received positive reviews for its imaginative and descriptive portrayal of space exploration, as well as its exploration of themes such as human connection and the desire for adventure. ==Full Text of the Novel== Wang Ximing, [[Lei Yangjuan]] and their son [[Wang Zhaochu]] are watching the starry sky on the top of Dingshan Park in [[Qidong]]. It was a beautiful night, the stars were twinkling and the moon was hanging in the sky. The family had just moved to the city, and stargazing had become their summer night activity.
Suddenly, they saw a very strange light. This light came from a distance, like a shooting star. However, this light did not land on the earth, but disappeared into the sky.
Both Wang Ximing and Lei Yangjuan were attracted by this strange light, and they wanted to know what it was. They followed the light for a distance, and finally came to a clearing. There, they saw an alien spaceship.
They were all stunned because they had never seen anything like this. They approached the craft to take a closer look. However, as they approached the spaceship, they heard a very strange sound. The sound seemed to come from inside the spaceship, and they were all taken aback.
This is an unusual night, and they are about to embark on a wonderful journey, an alien journey full of surprises and dangers.
Wang Ximing's research on aliens and UFOs made him feel no fear when facing this alien spaceship. Instead, he felt great excitement and curiosity. He couldn't wait to walk into the spaceship with Lei Yangjuan and Wang Zhaochu.
Once inside the ship, they were taken aback. The interior of this spaceship is unlike any car or building on Earth. Everything is smooth and transparent, with hardly any edges or crevices to be seen. They walked down a wide hallway surrounded by strange instruments and buttons. Wang Ximing looked at these instruments, trying to understand their functions.
Just when they were amazed, a ray of light suddenly flashed. They looked back to find an alien was appearing in front of them. The alien was a little different from what they had imagined. It was about 1.5 meters tall, with an oval body and a red spherical head without eyes, nose or mouth. It appears to be able to communicate with humans using its mind.
Wang Ximing was very excited about this alien, and he had a long communication with this alien. The alien told them it was from a planet called Kilvax and was on a scientific mission. They are very grateful to Wang Ximing's family for their curiosity, because it means that they can communicate more deeply with the people on Earth.
During this exchange, Wang Ximing learned a lot about aliens and the universe, such as aliens' observations of earth civilization, other life forms in the universe, their technological level, and so on. This allows Wang Ximing to have a deeper and broader understanding of the universe.
During this contact, Wang Ximing also invited this alien to come to the earth to explore our civilization and human society. The alien accepted the invitation, and also showed them some other wonderful things, such as virtual reality and photon technology. All this filled Wang Ximing and his family with surprise and excitement.
Wang Ximing felt a familiar excitement in his heart, because this was not his first contact with aliens. He was relieved to realize that the friendly alien wasn't hostile. Wang Ximing knew that a common language was needed to communicate with aliens, so he began to communicate with aliens in simple and easy-to-understand English.
The alien's language is an unfamiliar language, but Wang Ximing can understand it. They started communicating, talking about some things on earth. Aliens are very interested in the earth. Wang Ximing introduced to him the natural scenery of the earth, human history and culture, and some challenges faced by human beings. The aliens also shared their planet with Wang Ximing, as well as their exploration and discovery in the universe.
Although Wang Ximing had experienced an alien abduction incident, he had no sense of fear. Instead, he was full of curiosity about this exchange with aliens. He has always kept an open mind and is constantly exploring this mysterious universe. Communication with aliens not only made him excited, but also gave him a deeper understanding and understanding of the world he was in.
The language barrier between Wang Ximing and the aliens does exist, but the aliens seem to have an advanced translation device that can instantly translate any language. This allows them to communicate in simple English, although the alien's English may sound slightly accented.
Wang Ximing is very grateful for this translation device, and he keeps studying it, trying to understand how it works. This translation device is not like a normal translation machine, it is more like a small electronic device that can accurately capture the nuances of human language and translate it into a language that aliens can understand.
Although translation devices can ensure their conversations flow smoothly, some complex concepts and vocabulary still require more in-depth explanations. During this process, Wang Ximing will use gestures, simple diagrams or animations to help express his ideas. Sometimes he also uses language assistance tools, such as using the voice translation function on his mobile phone, or opening a web page to find relevant pictures and video materials to explain.
The aliens are also very patient, they will listen to Wang Ximing's explanation tirelessly, and will give a more in-depth explanation in their own language when necessary. This exchange of mutual understanding and respect allows them to establish a good way of communication and discuss more in-depth and interesting topics.
Wang Ximing was very excited because this was his dream for many years. But at the same time, he also knew that his idea might be a bit too risky. He began to think about how to express his thoughts to the aliens tactfully, because he didn't want the aliens to misunderstand his intentions or feel that he wanted to invade other planets. So, he cautiously began to express his thoughts to the aliens in simple English, and asked if they could help him go to the planet Kilvax in order to further explore the mysteries of the universe.
Wang Ximing's tone was very modest and cautious, because he knew that he should be more cautious when facing alien civilizations with high IQs. He explained to the aliens that he didn't want to invade or plunder other planets, but just wanted to gain a deeper understanding of the mysteries of the universe and look for other intelligent life that might exist. He also emphasized that he will abide by the regulations and requirements of aliens and try his best to avoid any damage to aliens or other planets.
The aliens seemed to understand Wang Ximing's thoughts and expressed that they would be happy to help him realize his wish. They explained some basics about space travel to Ximing Wang, and told him that they needed some time to prepare the relevant equipment and technology so that he could go to the planet Kilvax. Wang Ximing was very grateful and promised that he would cooperate with their plan as much as possible and wait for the aliens to prepare the relevant technology before proceeding.
On the one hand, Wang Ximing is very eager for this opportunity to go to Kilvax, but on the other hand, he also understands the worries and concerns of his family. He is very clear that his decision this time may cause great harm to his family, but he also knows that this is the only chance in his life. He felt himself facing an extremely difficult decision. He began to seriously consider how to appease his family and minimize the risk of this operation. He had in-depth communication and exchanges with his family members, trying to persuade them to agree with his decision.
"It's too dangerous, you go alone, I absolutely disagree!" Lei Yangjuan stood at the door of the bedroom and said firmly.
"Yes, Dad, you can't go, I don't want you to die." Wang Zhaochu looked at his father anxiously.
Wang Ximing sighed, looked at the two, and said seriously: "I know that such a trip is risky, but we have the opportunity to explore a whole new world, and I don't want to miss this opportunity."
"But, you can't take this risk. You have a family, and you have us." Lei Yangjuan had tears in her eyes.
Wang Ximing gently stroked Lei Yangjuan's shoulder and said softly: "I love you all, but this is my dream, maybe this is the last chance in my life. I need your support."
Lei Yangjuan looked into Wang Ximing's eyes, then at her son, thinking.
"Okay, but you must ensure your own safety, and we will also pray for you." Lei Yangjuan paused, and finally let go of her hand.
"Thank you, I will try my best to ensure safety." Wang Ximing said gratefully holding their hands.
Although he experienced some verbal conflicts, Wang Ximing finally got the understanding and support of his family.
Since then, the aliens and Wang Ximing have left contact information, but because the aliens do not have social accounts and network technology on earth, Wang Ximing does not know how the aliens contacted him. Two months later, when Wang Ximing received the notice from the aliens, he was very surprised and curious at the same time.
Wang Ximing recalled the conversation with the aliens, and he thought of a possible explanation: the communication methods of aliens and the earth may be different. So, he began to prepare to try some new methods.
Wang Ximing gave the aliens his e-mail address and phone number, and told them how to use the communication equipment on Earth. However, these methods did not work, as the aliens used technology that was completely different from that used on Earth.
Wang Ximing began to feel frustrated, but he did not give up. He began to imagine how the alien technology would work, and he speculated that the communication used by the aliens might be an advanced brain wave communication.
So he started researching brainwave communication technology and tried to create some simple brainwave communication devices. After weeks of trying, he finally succeeded. He discovers that, using these devices, he can communicate with aliens. He and the aliens discussed some details about the planet Kilvax, and finally finalized the trip plan.
The communication process was very difficult for Wang Ximing, but he overcame a series of technical and language difficulties, and finally established contact with the aliens. This also made him feel the diversity of technology and life forms in outer space, which made him extremely shocked and excited.
However, Wang Ximing began to feel anxious and confused, and he was not sure whether the aliens could understand his concerns. He decides to communicate with the aliens again, hoping to resolve his doubts.
Wang Ximing found the aliens and expressed his concerns in as simple English as possible: "I want to know, if I get to the Kilvax planet, can I survive? Because there is no air and food in outer space, I am worried that I will not be able to survive." .Besides, we can only communicate in simple English, and I'm worried that we won't be able to solve the problems we have. If you can't solve these problems, will you still take me to Kilvax?"
After the aliens listened, they communicated with Wang Ximing using complex electromagnetic wave signals: "We understand your concerns, but we can provide air and food suitable for human survival. In addition, we have a set of simple and effective communication methods that can make We can communicate in any situation. We will ensure your safety and comfort and provide you with everything you need."
Hearing the alien's answer, Wang Ximing breathed a sigh of relief, and he began to believe that the trip was worth the risk. He thanked the extraterrestrials for their care and help, and decided to actively prepare for the trip to the Kilvax planet.
A new problem appeared again: Wang Ximing knew the importance of keeping in touch with his family while traveling in outer space, but he felt very helpless in the face of network and communication restrictions. He began to think about how to solve this problem, but also realized that he needed to prepare for the worst.
Therefore, Wang Ximing began to actively look for some alternatives, including researching new ways to communicate with aliens, looking for some breakthroughs in communication technology, and exploring some new teleportation and transition technologies so that he can quickly return to Earth when needed. He kept thinking and exploring during his journey, trying to find a workable solution.
He also explored this issue with aliens, wondering if any technology could solve the communication problem. The aliens told him that they have an advanced communication device that can communicate over a long distance, and this device is very small and portable, so you can carry it with you. This surprised Wang Ximing, who felt that this was a very good solution.
So, Wang Ximing set off with this communication device. This device is in communication with the alien's ship and can send messages directly to Earth in order to keep in touch with his family and colleagues on Earth. The technology of this device is very advanced, and it can transmit information quickly, ensuring that his connection with the earth is unimpeded.
Although traveling in outer space will still face many risks and unknowns, Wang Ximing has a comfort in his heart: he will not be alone, he can keep in touch with his family and friends, and share his experience and exploration in outer space.
At this moment, Wang Ximing finally embarked on a journey to the Kilvax planet, full of anticipation and anxiety in his heart. He watched the earth and the solar system gradually shrink, and felt a little bit reluctant, but more of it was his curiosity and desire for the unknown universe. He saw many mysterious stars and cosmic scenes, and saw the unimaginable beauty and magnificence from the earth.
When the aircraft started to fly with curvature and entered the state of superluminal speed, he saw a beautiful and spectacular cosmic scene. He saw countless stars, twinkling in the black universe, some of which emitted light like shooting stars, across the pitch-black sky. Some stars form shining nebulae, like clouds floating in the depths of the universe. The gas in the nebula emits light of various colors, including red, yellow, blue, purple and so on.
In addition, Wang Ximing saw several mysterious stars, one of which was very large, like a giant crystal ball shining with light, and the other looked like a vortex, constantly rotating, as if to swallow everything around it. In addition, he also saw a huge nebula, shaped like a huge bird, with its wings spread and magnificent feathers displayed.
These scenes made Wang Ximing amazed. He felt as if he was in a mysterious, beautiful and infinite world. Such a cosmic scene made him feel incredible, and it also strengthened his belief in exploring the universe.
But over time, he began to feel anxious and lonely. In the distant universe, he felt small and alone. Although he communicated with the aliens in English more and more smoothly, he still found it difficult to adapt to this completely different life. He thought of his wife and son, and missed their company and support.
During his travels in outer space, aliens took Wang Ximing to visit many mysterious galaxies and planets, allowing him to witness many sights that humans have never seen before. When Wang Ximing was admiring a huge comet, the alien suddenly asked about the music on the earth. After Wang Ximing heard the alien's question, he immediately became very excited. He shared some of his favorite music and singers with the aliens, and also introduced some elements of traditional Chinese music to the aliens. The aliens were also very interested and asked Wang Ximing to play a piece of Chinese zither for him. This exchange made Wang Ximing forget the reluctance to leave the earth and the solar system, and it also made him get closer to aliens.
When Wang Ximing was observing a very mysterious planet, the alien suddenly asked him: "Are there any funny jokes on Earth? I want to hear a joke!"
Wang Ximing hesitated for a moment, wondering if aliens could understand human humor. But he still replied without hesitation: "Of course, I'll tell you a bad joke, I hope your smile won't freeze on your face."
The alien was a little confused: "What is a 'dirty joke'?"
Wang Ximing explained: "It's not funny, but it still makes people laugh."
"Oh, okay, come on, tell me one!" The alien said enthusiastically.
Wang Ximing said eloquently: "There was a snail who wanted to participate in the race, but the other snails laughed at him for being too slow, and finally he had to wear red shoes. When it was time for the race, the snails were all shouting, but only One snail had no sound. He looked at the snail next to him and asked, "Why don't you talk?" The snail replied, "I couldn't help laughing when I put on the red shoes!""
After listening to the alien, he was a little puzzled. He didn't know why he had to wear red shoes to laugh. But Wang Ximing's funny expression made him feel very funny, so he also giggled.
After that, Wang Ximing chatted with the alien about his favorite movie again, he said: "There is a movie called " ET", in which an alien accidentally fell on the earth and was rescued by a little boy. Then they became good friends and went on an adventure together, and finally the aliens returned to their own planet."
The alien looked bewildered, and Wang Ximing quickly explained: "This alien is very cute. His fingers are long and can emit light. Their planet is a very magical place, full of strange plants and animals. , very beautiful. And the friendship between the alien and the little boy is also very touching, and one cannot help but be moved."
The alien's eyes lit up, and he began to be interested in this movie. Wang Ximing continued to introduce: "There is also a movie called "The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy". Space adventure, I met a group of very interesting aliens. These aliens look very strange, some look like octopuses, and some stick to the ground like chewing gum, which is very funny.
After hearing this, the alien also began to laugh happily. Seeing the reaction of the aliens, Wang Ximing felt very happy. He knew that even if they were from different planets, they could use the common language of movies to communicate and communicate.
A strange and mysterious galaxy appeared in front of Wang Ximing's eyes, which could not be compared with any planet in the solar system. Under the guidance of the aliens, the spaceship passed through hundreds of planets and satellites of various shapes, some of which revolved around the planets, and some were scattered in the interstellar space. Wang Ximing felt that he was in a wonderful and strange universe.
When Wang Ximing's spacecraft passed by a green planet, he saw a group of alien creatures that looked like butterflies flying in the air with colorful lights shining on their wings. On another planet he saw a great pyramid soaring into the sky, and on another planet he saw a sea of crystal shards whose reflections dazzled the eye.
After a period of travel, the spacecraft finally landed on the planet Kilvax. Wang Ximing jumped down excitedly. This was the first time he set foot on the land of an alien planet.
He felt every cell in his body trembling and his heart beating faster. The scene around him felt very strange, every object and every creature he saw was something he had never seen before. He saw monsters bigger than any animal on the earth, they had all kinds of strange tentacles, wings and eyes, and strange gardens with colorful plants growing on them, unlike any kind on the earth.
Wang Ximing's extraterrestrial guide introduced him to various creatures on the Kilvax planet, as well as their habits and lifestyles. They saw a group of aliens with very high IQ, whose IQ even surpassed that of humans on Earth. They developed super intelligent machines and mastered many technologies beyond humans, such as time travel and teleportation.
On this planet, Wang Ximing felt a sense of mystery and strangeness beyond his imagination. Every discovery surprised him. He felt that this planet was like a world in a science fiction novel, full of infinite possibilities. Imaginative and exploratory.
On the Kilvax planet, Wang Ximing also learned how to use alien technology, including how to communicate with aliens and how to use alien weapons for defense. He also learned about the values and culture of aliens, which gave him a deeper understanding of the alien world.
Although the time Wang Ximing spent on Kilvax was very short, it will have a profound impact on his life. He realizes that outer space is an infinitely vast and unknown world, and he is full of hope and longing for the future.
's expedition on the Kilvax planet came to an end, so he returned to Earth by spaceship. After returning to Earth, Wang Ximing couldn't wait to tell his family and friends about his adventures in outer space. However, as he shared his story with family and friends, he found that his memories seemed so blurred that they seemed unreal.
Wang Ximing was very confused, he didn't understand why his memory was so blurred, as if he had never had it before. He began to feel anxious and restless, worried that he would go crazy. He went to the doctor, but the doctor told him everything was fine.
A few months later, Wang Ximing suddenly received a mysterious letter from the planet Kilvax. The letters told him that his experience did not happen by accident. He was chosen for the mission and had a chip implanted by aliens that recorded his memories, which were then erased upon his return to Earth. The letter told him that this mission was to help them find an alien who was exiled to the earth, and the whereabouts of this alien had been tracked by them. Finally, the letter told him that the alien was by his side.
This made Wang Ximing very shocked. He began to pay attention to the people and things around him, trying to find out who the exiled alien was. He starts to doubt everyone, including his family and friends. However, he did not find the answer in the end, and everything became blurred and uncertain. ==FULL VIDEO== [[File:ChatGPT|none|thumb|360x360px]] [[Category:Wang Ximing]] [[Category:Lei Yangjuan]] {{Navbox_Total}}

page.title: Wang Zhaochu's Super Long Winter Vacation

revision.text:
{{VlogInfo|title1=Wang Zhaochu's Happy Winter Vacation (2020)|image1=[[File:2020|480px]]|caption1=Screenshot of Wang Zhaochu's 2020 winter vacation documentary. |time = January 14th ~ February 23rd, 2020 |location = [[Qidong County]] | person = [[Wang Zhaochu]] | producer = [[Guo Jingxing]] | duration = 90 minutes | production time = February 26, 2020 | originally posted = March 1, 2020|publishing platform=[https://youtu.be/H7gE4j2-qFQ YouTube]|watch URL=https://youtu.be/H7gE4j2-qFQ|description=A special Wang Zhaochu documentary born in early 2020 when [[Wikipedia:COVID-19|COVID-19 Epidemic]] broke out }} '''''Wang Zhaochu's Super Long Winter Vacation''' ''(Chinese name: '''2020''')'','' also known as '''''Wang Zhaochu's 2020 Super Long Winter Vacation Five Days''''', is due to a special documentary born out of the [[Wikipedia:COVID-19|COVID-19 Epidemic]] outbreak in early 2020. The film was released online on streaming media platforms such as YouTube on March 1, 2020.
==Video Introduction== Lying comfortably on the sofa watching Ultraman Tiga, playing the Lucky Jar of Plants vs. Zombies, going to the Jiangnan Hotel to enjoy street video games, singing birthday songs for the elderly, shopping for clothes with parents, and riding shared electric vehicles, singing karaoke songs in Sanwang Garden, dancing horse-riding dance with uncle, and playing badminton with grandma... [[Wang Zhaochu]] and his uncles enjoyed a fulfilling and long winter vacation brought about by the epidemic. These videos were shot on 2020.1.14~2020.2.23. [[Jiaxing Radio Station]] took advantage of the epidemic to produce this documentary "''Wang Zhaochu - 2020 Super Long Winter Vacation Five Days of Joy''", which recorded the wonderful moments of [[Wang Zhaochu]].
==Full Video== [[File:2020]] ==Wonderful selection== ===Episode 1 (January 14th~January 16th)=== Wang Zhaochu watched Ultraman, played Plants vs. Zombies, and went to Jiangnan Hotel to play street video games, etc.: [https://youtu.be/-9Maa3Kbq4U Watch on YouTube] === Episode 2 (January 17) === Wang Zhaochu helped his old man (who passed away on September 24, 2020) celebrate his 84th birthday, sang birthday songs, played hide-and-seek with Rongrong, etc.: [https://youtu.be/ni-_osATx90 Watch on YouTube] ===Episode 3 (January 18~January 22)=== Wang Zhaochu and his father are shopping downstairs, setting off fireworks, firecrackers and receiving couriers, traveling to Qidong central market, shopping, crying when they come back, etc.: [https://youtu.be/4vq06tZgWug Watch on YouTube] === Episode 4 (January 31st ~ February 20th) === BBQ downstairs, go to Sanwang Garden to sing karaoke, play games with Wang Ziyu, etc.: [https://youtu.be/IuLrcXspQ1A Watch on YouTube] ===Episode 5 (February 21st ~ February 23rd)=== Wang Zhaochu is playing games, trampoline, horseback riding, badminton, etc. at home: [https://youtu.be/WEZV45mZUHk Watch on YouTube] == Video Trivia MV == [[File: Spring Wind Official MV]] [[Category:Wang Zhaochu]] [[Category:Qidong]] [[Category:COVID-19]] [[Category:Vlog]] [[Category:2020Vlog]] [[zh:2020]] {{Navbox_Total|state5=expanded}}

[[zh:(2020)]] {{Stub}}{{MVInfo|image1=[[File:MV - Big Fishcover ]]|producer=Guo Jingxing|production date=August 13, 2020|person= Wang Ziyu, Wang Zhaochu, Wang Ximing, etc. | date range = before August 13, 2020 | Release date = May 20, 2016 | format = MP3 |type=Chinese Pop|duration=5:12|record label=Supreme Records|lyricist=Tang Tian|composer=Ma Jing|title1=Big Fish|title=Big Fish|caption1=Screenshot of Wang Ziyu's MV "Big Fish". }}
'''''Big Fish''''' (Chinese name: '''''') is a cover song of '''[[Wang Ziyu]]''' in 2020. The song was recorded and produced by [[Guo Jingxing]], the MV was shot and edited by [[Guo Jingxing]], and the song was recorded in [[Wang Ziyu]]'s bedroom on the evening of August 12, 2020.
== Song Details == "Big Fish" is a song written by Yin Yue, composed by Qian Lei, and sung by Zhou Shen. It is the impression song of the animated movie "Big Fish and Begonia". It was first released on May 20, 2016. In September 2016, the song won the Top Ten Golden Melody Awards at the annual festival of the Asian New Song List.
=== Creative Background === "Big Fish" is a film impression song tailored by Yin Yue and Qian Lei for "Big Fish and Begonia". new ideas arose. In order to allow Zhou Shen to interpret the emotion of the song more accurately when singing, the lyricist Yin Yue told Zhou Shen the meaning of the lyrics and the stories behind the lyrics one by one. During the recording process, Yin Yue decided to let Zhou Shen sing with himself in the last part of the song in order to sublimate his feelings.<ref>https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A4%A7%E9%B1%BC/19675903</ref>
=== Song Appreciation === The main song part of the song has a long and long melody, and the lyrics are rich in imagery and full of moving details. The transition from the magnificent scene to the delicate emotion is like a poem that directly touches people's hearts. The melody of the chorus gradually rises, vast and ethereal, and the lyrics directly express Chun's emotions, with a bit of classical sadness in traditional Chinese culture, making people intoxicated by the music and stories of "Big Fish". Zhou Shen is known for his unique voice and delicate singing. His singing in "Big Fish" is as clean as ever, from low-pitched singing and eloquent narration to long and passionate, rich in layers and consistent with deep affection. "Big Fish" Zhongchun, Kun, and Qiu's complex emotional fate is sung delicately, ethereally and movingly. Whether it is lyrics or singing, the impression song "Big Fish" is in the same line with the connotation of "Big Fish and Begonia". Like the national style of the movie, the song also inherits the long-standing style of Chinese music, and the lingering sound is endless.
The version sung by Wang Ziyu is the version sung by Zhou Shen.

[[zh:]] '''Steve's Big Adventure in the Universe''' is the "Minecraft" version of the movie script written by [[Wang Ziyu]] in 2019, but it has not been made into a movie yet.
==Main characters and dubbing== '''Herobrine (Herobrine)'''[[Wang Ziyu]] Dubbing '''Robber (Robber)'''[[Guo Jingxing]] Dubbing '''Alien (Steve)''' - Dubbed by Jun Jun '''Police, Good Friends (Cops)''' - Voiced by Liu Haizhao
==The general plot of the story== ===Scene 1=== '''Hero Brun, the incarnation of justice, saved the child but was beaten into outer space''' A man (''don't know who'') hurts a child, and Hero Brun sees it. With Hero Brun's righteous heart, he decided to save the child; At this time, Hero Brun stepped forward to fight against the bad guys. The child saw it at this time, and was very surprised. He quickly got up and called 911 (110) to call the police. At this time the police came. When they first arrived, they were still fighting, but because the villain was so powerful, he beat the police to Mars (''whatever star''). ===Scene Two=== '''Police encounters on Mars''' (''On Mars'') Because there are probes of Jupiter aliens on Mars, the aliens on Jupiter discovered him at this time, thinking that it was soldiers sent by humans to investigate and kill the aliens. The aliens rushed over at this time, shot fireballs from their hands, and the police were blown away. Then the police were beaten into the void. (''On Earth'') Hero Brun's eyes were red, and after knocking down the bad guys, he flew to Mars again, (''On Mars'') to see what happened to the police, but found that the police were dead up. Helobrun got even angrier. He knelt there, not noticing that the alien next to him was making fireballs. The aliens knocked Helobrun into the void, but Helobrun had flying claws, so he caught the alien directly. The starman went down with him. Throw the alien into the void, and use the flying claws to grab a stone above Mars, then fly up again, and come back here again. ===Scene III=== '''Hello Brunn avenges a good friend''' Because it was the alien who killed the policeman, and then changed the policeman to its good friend, that is, killed his good friend, because the alien killed his good friend Man, and then he went to investigate Uranus, Neptune, Mars, and Jupiter , as long as there is an alien, he must be eliminated, because the alien killed his companion, so he wants to kill the alien. ===Act Four=== '''Hello Brun returns to justice and saves the wounded''' After killing, Hero Brun returned to the earth and found that the houses on the earth were all empty and destroyed. The houses were not as many houses as before, but some ashes with fire burning on them. Brun heard a cry of help, and kept looking for where the sound was coming from. (At this time, Helobrun added the function of Shunfeng ear) Then Herobrun used Shunfeng ear to hear where the sound came from, and then turned on the teleportation function, and then it happened that the person was covered in blood, and one eye was missing , The eyeballs fell. Helobrun tried his best to pull him out, just wanted to use the flying claw to get the stone off, and the man was saved. ===Scene Five=== '''Hello Brun rebuilds the earth and recalls the past''' Then Hero Brun tried every means to restore the earth to have many houses, because the aliens were destroyed, and then Hero Brun made a house by himself, lived there for one night, and then made the city tomorrow. good. After tens of thousands of years, all the houses were finally built, but Helobrun was the only one. In another 10,000 years, Helobrun would raise cubs, and there would be about 100 million babies just like Helobrun. people. Because there are many houses for them to live in. At this time, Hero Brun thought of the former friend, the friend who was killed by aliens. He entered a house, and he imagined that his friend was sitting and watching TV at his house. His friend saw Helobrun waving to him, and then Helobrun hugged him. He didn't know it was a fantasy, and then he regretted it. "'''Wang Zhaochu'''" (Chinese name: ''''''), is a 2017 National Day drama produced by '''[[Jiaxing Films]]''' This documentary was produced from August 1 to August 31, 2017. It recorded some video and photo moments from 1965 to July 2017. Although the title of the film is '''''[[Wang Zhaochu]]''''', but The actual recording of Wang Zhaochu's video is only in the second half of the movie. The documentary tells part of the experience of my friends and relatives in the way of event flow and first-person perspective, with [[Guo Jingxing]] as the first-person perspective, most of the videos in the video were shot by [[Guo Jingxing]] himself, in order to record life bit by bit.
The film was released in Hengyang City, [[Wikipedia:Hunan|Hunan Province]] [[Qidong County]] on October 1, 2017. On October 7, 2018, the video was released on [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=durCJsSyEtk YouTube].
==Movie Details== === Stories of the last century (1965.5-1984.10) === In May of the lunar calendar in 1965, Uncle [[Wang Wuhong|Wuhong]] was born in Taihe Hall, and in September of the same year, Aunt Guo Xinhua was born in Huangtupu.
In 1970, the blue sky and white clouds were used as quilts, and the wild grass was used as tapestry. The high mountains set up sentries for me, and the flowing water of the Xiangjiang River lulls me to sleep!
This photo was taken by my uncle in the countryside during the period of reform and opening up. She was only 14 years old at the time. After graduating from junior high school, due to family conditions, she dropped out of school and stayed at home to do farm work for the family.
Maybe it was the marriage bestowed on them by God. One night, Uncle [[Wang Wuhong|Wuhong]] asked Uncle Xinhua to watch a movie in the countryside. A few days later, they were farming and planting rice seedlings together, so they walked together.
Time unknowingly went to 1984, when the whole country was celebrating, and it happened to be in this At that time, Uncle also got married.
They lived in a newly built two-story bungalow in Shanmuqiao, and the photo I see now was taken outside the bungalow.
===My story with Wang Jiaming and Lei Yangjuan (2012.1-2014.8)=== On January 4, 2012, [[Wang Jiaming]] and I used a relatively advanced mobile phone at that time when the photography equipment was relatively backward. I dont remember the brand and model. The first program Opera 2, this video is a precious picture recorded by the 35mm camera at that time, and it also marks the beginning of video recording by [[Wang Jiaming]] and me.
3 days later, [[Wang Jiaming]] and I recorded this physical experiment, and [[Wang Jiaming]] and I were out of curiosity at that time, in order to record this video of the miraculous phenomenon that water was sucked into the cup at that time It also recorded the most classic scene in our filming history.
Afterwards, we successively recorded a series of physical experiments and many songs, making 2012 the peak year of video shooting.
Since the advent of professional cameras, the video we shoot has entered the era of high-definition video. However, at this time, [[Wang Jiaming]] put forward his idea of shooting movies.
I remember the first time I saw my sister-in-law, it was February 2013, I remember that I went to eat with Mingming and [[Wang Jiaming]], and Yuanyuan and the others seemed to be in a coffee shop The restaurant is newly opened, and the business is good, so I sat down.
At that time, I suddenly had such an idea, yes, I didnt think too much about it, because the song was very popular and catchy at the time, and then I had this idea, I just came back from Shenzhen, and I was idle at home. Do.
===Stories of Wang Ximing and Lei Yangjuan (2015.1-2016.2)=== On February 14, 2015, [[Wang Ximing]] and [[Lei Yangjuan]] arrived in Qidong by train. After getting their marriage certificate that evening, there was this video, [[Lei Yang] Juan]] said that when queuing up, it happened to be the last one of the day.
Four months later, I'm here again. On June 20, 2015, Uncle [[Wang Wuhong|Wuhong]]'s 50th birthday, colleagues on the construction site came to congratulate him.
On July 25, 2015, [[Lei Yangjuan]] and [[Wang Ximing]] returned to Qidong. [[Wang Ximing]] bought a new computer, and he is checking the condition of the computer, and [[Lei Yangjuan]] also brought a gift to the family after returning this time.
On October 28, this gift broke out, and [[Wang Zhaochu]] was born.
===The story of the Spring Festival in 2016 (2016.2)=== On February 10, 2016, because Guo Jianchen and Zhou Qian got married and held a wedding ceremony, my uncle accompanied me to book a table at Grandma Bridge Hotel in the central market, while [[Wang Ximing]] and the others took care of their children at home.
===The story after the 2016 college entrance examination (2016.6-2016.10)=== On June 7, 2016, [[Wang Jiaming]] and I entered the college entrance examination room, and we are about to usher in one of the most important turning points in our lives. According to reports, this years college entrance examination is called the most rigorous college entrance examination in history, and the tension exaggerated by the media Under the atmosphere, I hoped that I could show my ideal level in the college entrance examination. The moment I stepped into the examination room, I realized that the college entrance examination was actually not as strict as I imagined before. Talking and laughing, after the math test in the afternoon, most people looked dignified after leaving the test room. Math is difficult, and I am no exception. After the English exam the next afternoon, my high school life came to an end.
On June 17, 2016, my aunt brought 8-month-old [[Wang Zhaochu]] to play.
On July 6, 2016, [[Wang Jiaming]], [[Wang Jiaming]] father and [[Wang Ziyu]] and I came to visit Siming Mountain. When we found this creek, [[Wang Ziyu]] always made new discoveries. The curiosity of exploring the creek prompted us to move forward and go to deeper streams.
In September 2016, [[Wang Jiaming]] and I walked into the university campus. The first thing we did after entering the university was the military parade. After the 22 days of military training, the National Day is coming. On October 1, Uncle and the others came to play in Qidong. At this time, Wang Zhaochu was already able to walk under the traction of the rope.
===The story of the Spring Festival in 2017 (2017.1-2017.2)=== On January 30, 2017, [[Wang Ximing]] and I went to Shaoshan, a famous red tourist spot in Hunan and the hometown of Mao Zedong. This is the scene at a local restaurant at noon that day.
In the afternoon, we set off to Shaoshan Scenic Area, which is in the Shaoshan Mao Zedong Museum. We saw the great achievements along the way in the history of the founding of the country. In the evening, we decided to go to Changsha Underwater World to play.

[[zh:2018]] {{Stub}}{{Movie|title1=3-day Tour to Western Hunan in 2018|image1=xiangxi.jpg|caption1=Xiangxi Documentary Poster (February 2018). |Origin={{China}} |language = Simplified Chinese ([[Qidong]] dialect) |release date = February 22, 2018 |director=Wang Yonghong |producer = Wang Yonghong [[Guo Jingxing]] |screenwriter = Wang Yonghong [[Wang Jiaming]] [[Guo Jingxing]] |Actor=[[Wang Ziyu]] Wang Yonghong [[Guo Jingxing]] [[Wang Jiaming]] Shi Hongmei Zhou Sitong Guo Manyuan | Length = 67 minutes (before modification) 62 minutes (modified) |distributor=Jiaxing Pictures|budget=US$560|box office=[[Qidong]]:10 RMB|Mainland China=2018 Spring Festival Three-day Tour|Hong Kong=Spring Festival Bliss Tour: My 2018|Taiwan=2018 Spring Festival three-day tour|[[Qidong]]=visit Xiangxi}} '''''3-day Tour to Western Hunan in 2018''''' (Chinese name: '''2018''') was released in [[Qidong]] during the Spring Festival in 2018, it is a documentary film based on casual shooting to record the scenery of western Hunan. After modification, the duration is 62 minutes. It is Jiaxing Satellite TVs first true documentary. video. This documentary was filmed by [[Guo Jingxing]] with his mobile phone, and it is the whole journey of [[Guo Jingxing]] and [[Wang Jiaming]]s family in Xiangxi (mainly Zhangjiajie and Phoenix Ancient City) during the Spring Festival in 2018. "The Memories of Wang and Guo" and "A Trip to Shenzhen" are another objective and realistic tourist documentary. The video was produced by [[Guo Jingxing]]. After the film was broadcast in [[Qidong]], It was corrected by Wang Yonghong pointed out that the subtitle was wrong. The video was launched on the Tencent video website in mainland China with a bit rate of standard definition. Previously, high-definition videos could be watched on YouTube. ==Documentary Background== In January 2018, Wang Yonghong proposed the idea of traveling to Zhangjiajie during the Spring Festival. At that time [[Wang Jiaming]] told [[Guo Jingxing]] about it, but he did not form a final idea, it was just a proposal. On February 16, 2018, [[Wang Jiaming]] and his family temporarily decided to travel to Zhangjiajie. At that time, [[Wang Jiaming]]s family and [[Guo Jingxing]] made a preliminary agreement on this matter. A preliminary plan was made. On the 17th, [[Guo Jingxing]] and [[Wang Jiaming]] and their family got into their car, and Guo Manyuan joined them along with Wang Ziyu and Zhou Sitong. Arrive in Zhangjiajie at night. On the 18th, [[Wang Jiaming]] and his family decided to go to Tianmen Mountain Forest Park. After arriving at 9:00 in the morning, they went all the way forward and played the ladder and glass path, but they did not see the real scenery of Tianmen Mountain because of the rainy weather. At 14 o'clock, we had lunch at a restaurant at the foot of Tianmen Mountain. In the evening, we went to Zhangjiajie's most famous scenic spot - the Glass Bridge, and stayed in a nearby hotel. On the morning of the 19th, due to the sold-out tickets for the Glass Bridge and [[Wang Jiaming]]s initiative to petition against not entering the Glass Bridge, the group discussed together and planned to go to Fenghuang, another famous cultural tourism ancient city in western Hunan, and arrived at Fenghuang at 3 p.m. County, and enjoyed local cultural programs with Tujia and Miao characteristics in Western Hunan. On the 20th, the group went to the tourist attractions in Western HunanFenghuang County Waterfall and the South Great Wall, and returned to [[Qidong]] County in the afternoon.

'''''Alien Revelation''''' (Chinese name: '''''') was published in October 2016 by '''[[Wang Ximing]]''', which is an opinion piece about [[Wikipedia:alien|Alien]]. This point of view points out that aliens are hidden among human beings, but human beings forget that they are aliens. ==Full Text== Speaking of aliens, I agree with the view that we ourselves are aliens. Therefore, aliens have the same appearance as us, and they hide among us humans. Why can't aliens be discovered so far, but there are so many evidences of aliens' existence. Aliens migrated to the earth a long time ago, and time has passed for a long time, and the aliens on the earth have forgotten that they are from an alien planet. And the home planet of the aliens still remembers this incident, so they come to the earth to see it from time to time, so there are many [[Wikipedia:UFO|ufo]] events, and the aliens have the same appearance as us, mixing among us, So aliens can never be found. That's my point. The so-called human beings evolved from microorganisms is just a cover for aliens. ==Supplement== On November 7, 2019, [[Wang Ximing]] supplemented this point of view with the following additions:
Why don't aliens show up? This question has always been wrong. Humans are aliens.

page.title: That Night, at Two O'Clock in the Morning in Shenzhen

revision.text:
'''''That Night, at Two O'Clock in the Morning in Shenzhen''''' is a narrative article published by [[Wang Ximing]] in 2012. The article has a total of 690 words and describes the scene of Wang Ximing working in Shenzhen. However, Wang Ximing did not finish this article in 2012. Later, on August 12, 2015, Wang Ximing completed the supplementary writing of the article.
==Full Article== That day, at two o'clock in the morning, I was still sitting in front of the computer, and it was raining faintly outside the window, and the raindrops fell on the window sill, making a ticking, ticking sound. I got up and stood by the window, looking at the brightly lit urban area of Shenzhen over there, took out a cigarette from my pocket, lit it, took a deep breath, and let it out slowly. Watch the smoke swirl and slowly drift away with the wind...
The rain is still falling, the wind is still blowing, and the rain is slowly getting bigger. The small raindrops, after just a few minutes, become like a gaping embankment. I still stood by the window, silently watching the rain poured on the window sill and splashed on my body. As my thoughts went further and further away, I could no longer feel my own existence, and gradually felt that my body was getting lighter and lighter. I tried to raise my head, and saw a crescent moon, which was like a crescent eyebrow hanging lightly, a little strange, but also A little kind, I asked myself in a low voice, how long has it been since I looked up at the starry sky? How long has it been since I stared at this beautiful moon so carefully? At this moment, let the moonlight like water, the brilliance like sand pour down on my body gently, and touch my soul gently. The moonlight is like water, the stars are like sand, and the night is gentle. I felt that I had been sublimated, and a voice slowly came to my ears: You are so intoxicated, please stay! I suddenly came to my senses, my whole body was soaked, I heard the sound of high heels coming from behind, from far to near. Tick tock, one sound hit my heart, I want to turn back, but I can't control my body.
The sound was getting closer and closer, and it stopped behind me. Someone was stroking my hair, the movements were very gentle, but the hands were cold. I stood there blankly, my whole body was stiff, my limbs were cold, suddenly I wanted to laugh, laugh out loud! Laughing away the fear in my heart, the ignorance behind the joke, far away I saw the light shining in the rain, but I know that light does not belong to the world, I may die soon! I felt the heat of the light, and a huge heat hit my face. At this time, I was like a watchman, watching the coming of death and the end of my own life. As the light approached, the sound of high heels going away came from behind, and my body could also move slowly. I slowly turned my head and looked at the sound of going away, and what I saw was pitch black. The sense of fear in my mind doubled. Why is the light outside the window so strong? But it can't get into my room? I picked up the fruit knife next to me and turned around suddenly, only to see that the light that was far away was close at hand, and I couldn't see anything. There was a vast expanse of white in front of me, and darkness behind. I fell to the floor and passed out. I don't know how long it took before I opened my eyes, and my blurred vision gradually became clear. I saw a person standing beside me with a knife stuck in my chest. The heart-piercing pain lasted for a few seconds. Like smoke, it slowly floats into the air and disperses with the wind.
I have always wanted to float. In my dream, I floated into the air, passing fields, mountains and rivers, and forests. The feeling of forest tops brushing my toes is still fresh in my memory. It feels so good to float, empty, gently, all the turbidity in the whole body is removed, leaving a tulle-like body, a gossamer-like breath, flickering, flickering, flickering among the white clouds under the blue sky above everything...

{{VlogInfo|title1=Travel in Guangzhou 2019(Vlog)|image1=[[File:2019]]|caption1="Travel in Guangzhou 2019" trailer. |time = February 7th to February 9th, 2019|location = Guangzhou Baiyun Mountain, Sacred Heart Cathedral, Chimelong Paradise | person = [[Wang Jiaming]], [[Guo Jingxing]], Wang Wuhong, Shi Hongmei, [[Wang Ziyu]], Guo Manyuan | producer = Guo Jingxing | duration = total duration 29:29 (average 10 minutes for each episode) | production time = February 8th ~ February 26th, 2019 | release time = February 2020 26th | release platform = YouTube, Odysee | watch URL = https://youtu.be/tOqVds5vARI | event = Take the ropeway, climb the Guangzhou Tower, play in the amusement park}} '''''Travel in Guangzhou 2019''''' (Chinese name: '''2019''') is a Vlog produced by [[Jiaxing Films]] in 2019, filmed by Guo Jingxing, directed and produced by Wang Yonghong. The film is divided into a general episode and a diversity episode (3 episodes). The general process of the film is that [[Wang Jiaming]] and [[Guo Jingxing]] set off from Hengyang on February 7, 2019 and arrived in Guangzhou. They sat down at noon on February 8. The cable car arrived at the top of Baiyun Mountain, and then took a sightseeing car down the mountain. In the afternoon, we departed from the Sacred Heart Cathedral and arrived at the Canton Tower. The next day we came to Guangzhou Chimelong.
==Diversity Introduction== '''The following is taken from YouTube:''' ===Episode 1=== Wang Jiaming's family and Guo Jingxing set off from Hengyang on February 7, 2019, took a sleeper car for 6 hours along the way, and arrived in Guangzhou at 10 pm. The weather in Guangzhou was more than 20 degrees, while the weather in Hengyang was only 2 degrees Celsius. We felt very uncomfortable in the car, and then we arrived at the hotel next to the train station and stayed overnight. The next day (February 8) we started the Baiyun Mountain cableway tour.
Looking down from the Baiyun Mountain cableway, you can see overlapping peaks, criss-crossing streams, lush forests, singing birds and fragrant flowers.
===Episode 2=== Wang Jiaming's family and Guo Jingxing took the cableway to the top of Baiyun Mountain in Guangzhou at noon on February 8, 2019, then took a sightseeing bus down the mountain and took the subway to the Sacred Heart Cathedral.
Looking down from the top of Baiyun Mountain, you can see overlapping peaks and ridges, criss-cross streams, lush forests, singing birds and fragrant flowers.
The Sacred Heart Cathedral stands majestically, with carved beams and painted buildings, magnificent and beautiful.
===Episode 3=== Wang Jiaming's family and Guo Jingxing's father set off from the Sacred Heart Cathedral on the afternoon of February 8, 2019, arrived at the Canton Tower, and arrived at Guangzhou Chimelong the next day.

revision.text:
{{Stub}}{{VlogInfo|title1=One-day tour to Guiyang, Qiyang|image1=[[File:VLOG]]|caption1=Travel vlog on YouTube. |time = Afternoon of February 14, 2021|location = Qiyang Shuanglong Gorge, Guiyang Zhuangyuan Bridge|person = [[Wang Jiaming]], [[Wang Ziyu]], Wang Yonghong, Wang Wuhong, [[Guo Jingxing]], Shi Hongmei| producer=[[Guo Jingxing]]|duration=9:06|soundtrack=Stealing Gong, Bazaar, Just Blue|production time=February 17, 2021|release time=February 17, 2021|publishing platform= YouTube, Youku, Odysee|watch URL=https://youtu.be/XrwPi9FG8Fo}} '''''Travel to Double-Dragon Canyon in Qiyang and Zhuangyuan Bridge in Guiyang in 2021''''' (Chinese name: '''2021'''), Also known as '''Shuanglong Gorge One-Day Tour''', '''Guiyang One-Day Tour''', '''Qiyang Guiyang One-Day Tour''', it was published by [[Jiaxing Radio Station]] in 2021 A travel Vlog produced in February 2019, the film was filmed by [[Guo Jingxing]] and directed by Wang Yonghong. The video was filmed on February 14, 2021 and will be available on YouTube on February 17, 2021.
==Introduction to Tourist Attractions== [[Qidong]] Shuanglong Gorge is located between Hengqi Village, Guiyang Town, [[Qidong County]], Huaxi New Village, Meixi Town, Qiyang County, and Mubing Formation. The Longxi River flows into the Xiangjiang River from Huaxi Xincun to Muzhu Formation to Hengqi Village, Guiyang Town. This section of the canyon is long and winding, with beautiful scenery. It is a good outdoor place for leisure, adventure and adventure. Qidong Shuanglongxia Scenic Area is located at the junction of the southeast border of Qidong County and Qiyang, on the north bank of the middle reaches of the Xiangjiang River. It is 40 kilometers away from [[Qidong]] county seat, and 7 kilometers away from the urban area of Guiyang Town.
Zhuangyuan Bridge is located in Guiyang Town [[Qidong County]], Hengyang City. It is a 5-hole stone arch bridge with a length of 86.1 meters, a height of 9 meters, and a bridge deck width of 7.95 meters. . There are 20 long stone pillars on both sides, and 24 Tongxin bridge pavilions are built on the bridge deck, with a firm structure and a generous shape. In the middle of the bridge pavilion, there is a plaque of "Eternal Never Grinding". There is a pair of stone lions at the head of the bridge, which are mighty and majestic.
According to legend, when the stone bridge was built, there happened to be a champion of the new discipline passing by here. At that time, there were crowds of people at both ends of the bridge. From then on, he must recite poems and write poems, have feelings, and do something. What does the champion think?" The champion pondered for a while, and said happily: "Xiaosheng Xinzhong, and then he will be an official. He should serve the country and benefit the people. , not for profit. The elders dont have to worry. Everyone praised it as wonderful, so it was named Zhuangyuan Bridge. And erect a stone tablet at the south end of Zhuangyuan Bridge, engrave this couplet on the bridge plinth, and engrave the origin of Zhuangyuan Bridge on the stone tablet to remember its prosperity.
Zhuangyuan Bridge is also known as Xianren Bridge. There is another touching story about the origin of the name: it is said that there were exactly one hundred stonemasons working during the construction of the bridge, but only ninety-nine people were present at each meal. The "immortal" on the table helps. Therefore, the bridge was named "Xianren Bridge". On the stone slab of the bridge deck, we saw a depression that resembled footprints. The local people said that it was left by the immortals who helped them ascend to the sky after the completion of the bridge. Everyone called it "immortal feet". There is a "fairy's foot" on the stone pavement of the bridge deck, which is 28 cm long and 16 cm wide, which is about the size of a human foot. Visitors passing by here will always step on the "fairy's feet" with bare feet, so as to gain blessings and longevity[2]. The Zhuangyuan Bridge is all made of bluestones. Each square stone weighs several tons, and the lightest ones weigh several hundred kilograms. There is no adhesive material between the stones. Although they have experienced 130 years of wind and rain, they are still solid and firm. Under the conditions at that time, how these giant stones were transported to the building position and how they were built together is really unimaginable. No wonder later generations attribute the achievements of bridge construction to the help of immortals.
Zhuangyuan Bridge is a provincial key cultural relic protection unit and a famous scenic spot of Henggui Ancient Road in Hengyang City. It is located in the center of Guiyang Town and crosses the Baihe River into the Xiangjiang River. Zhuangyuan Bridge was first built in the Wanli period of the Ming Dynasty and rebuilt in the Tongzhi period of the Qing Dynasty (1862-1874). The bridge was submerged in floods. In the second year of Guangxu in the Qing Dynasty (1876), there was a squire named Yang Changshou who raised funds for the construction, and everyone responded with donations. In the eighth year of Guangxu in the Qing Dynasty, the bridge was completed, a bridge association was set up, and land was set up for long-term management. The Bridge Association once leased 24 bridge pavilions to small traders, set up shops on both sides of the bridge, and the rent collected was used to set up the local Yangsi Primary School. In the 33rd year of the Republic of China (1944), the Japanese invaders bombed the bridge twice with planes, but the bombs were all inaccurate. The bridge body was unharmed, but all 24 bridge pavilions were burned down, and the stone lions at the bridgehead were bombed until only the stone seat remained. In 1952, the people's government allocated funds for reconstruction. The bridge deck was first accessible to cars, but the rear bridge pavilion was demolished due to its low height, and 19 new bridge pavilions were built for cars to pass through. The bridge has been protected as a cultural relic and motor vehicles are prohibited from passing.

'''''Secret Monk Clothes''''' was created by '''''New Bing''''' on March 1, 2023 based on Internet search results this funny novel, the protagonists are '''[[Wang Ximing]]''', '''[[Lei Yangjuan]]''', '''[[Wang Zhaochu]]'''. This novel was generated under '''New Bing''''s ''More Creative'' Model.
== Novel Summary == This is a story that happened in a temple. [[Wang Ximing]] and [[Wang Zhaochu]] came to visit a master in the temple, but accidentally traveled half an hour into the future. They experienced many strange things in the next half hour, but finally heard the bell and returned to the present. During the period, they met [[Lei Yangjuan]], and together they explored how to solve the problem of [[Wang Ximing]] and [[Wang Zhaochu]] returning to the present. In the end, [[Wang Ximing]] and [[Wang Zhaochu]] returned to the present safely and returned the clothes to the master.
== Full Text of the Novel == [[Wang Ximing]] is a middle-aged man who loves photography. He often takes his son [[Wang Zhaochu]] to various places to take pictures. One day, they came to an ancient temple, and [[Wang Ximing]] wanted to take a photo of [[Wang Zhaochu]] wearing a monk's uniform, so he found an old monk in the temple and asked him to borrow one clothing.
The old monk agreed, but he said: "There is a rule about this dress. It can only be worn for half an hour, neither more nor less, otherwise there will be bad consequences."
[[Wang Ximing]] agreed, and then changed [[Wang Zhaochu]] into monk clothes. [[Wang Zhaochu]] was very cute in monk clothes, [[Wang Ximing]] was busy taking pictures of him, and it took more than half an hour before he knew it.
At this time, the old monk suddenly appeared in front of them, and said in horror, "Give me back the clothes quickly! Do you know what you have done?"
[[Wang Ximing]] asked puzzledly: "What did we do?"
The old monk said: "It's too late for you to wear my clothes! This dress is a relic left to me by my master. It has a secret: it can let the wearer go back to the past or the future for half an hour!"
"What?!" [[Wang Ximing]] exclaimed, "Then when are we now?"
The old monk said: "You are now half an hour in the future!"
"Then what should we do?" [[Wang Ximing]] asked.
The old monk said: "There is no way! You can only wait for half an hour before returning to the present! But you have to be careful, many things may happen in the next half hour!"
"Like what?" [[Wang Ximing]] asked.
The old monk said: "For example..." He pointed to the distance, "For example, [[Lei Yangjuan]] drove the car that drove over! Is she your wife? She just came back from the city, and she wants to Come to find you!"
"Ah?!" [[Wang Ximing]] turned pale with shock, "Then what shall we do? What will she think when she sees us dressed like this?"
The old monk said: "I don't know either! Hurry up and hide! Don't let her see it!"
[[Wang Ximing]] and [[Wang Zhaochu]] hurried to the backyard of the temple and hid in a remote corner. They wait nervously for half an hour to pass, hoping to be back in the present.
[[Lei Yangjuan]] drove to the gate of the temple. When she got off the car, she saw the old monk and asked, "Master, may I ask where my husband [[Wang Ximing]] and son [[Wang Zhaochu]] are?" where?"
As soon as the old monk saw [[Lei Yangjuan]], he remembered what happened just now. He was startled and didn't know what to say. He could only say vaguely, "They...they are here."
"Where is it?" [[Lei Yangjuan]] asked, "Why didn't I see it?"
The old monk said: "They...they are over there." He pointed in a random direction.
[[Lei Yangjuan]] followed the gestures of the old monk, but only saw a group of young monks fighting. She felt very strange, so she asked, "Master, are you sure it's over there?"
The old monk said, "Yes, it's over there."
[[Lei Yangjuan]] said: "But I only see a group of young monks."
The old monk said, "Oh... that... actually..."
"Actually what?" [[Lei Yangjuan]] asked.
The old monk said: "Actually... your husband and son are two of the young monks!"
"What?!" [[Lei Yangjuan]] exclaimed, "What are you kidding?!"
The old monk said: "I'm not kidding! It's true! Your husband and son became little monks after wearing my clothes! This dress has magic power! It can take the wearer back to the past or half a year in the future Hour!"
"You are talking nonsense!" [[Lei Yangjuan]] said incredulously, "How could such a thing happen? Return my husband and son to me!"
The old monk said: "I want to return it to you too! But not now! They have to wait for half an hour before they can be restored! Otherwise, there will be bigger troubles!"
[[Lei Yangjuan]] said: "Bigger trouble? What bigger trouble?"
The old monk said: "Don't you know? This dress is a relic left to me by my master. It has a secret: it can allow the wearer to go back to the past or the future for half an hour, but if the wearer is within half an hour If you dont change your clothes, you will stay in that time and space forever!
"Ah?!" [[Lei Yangjuan]] became even more frightened, "Then why did you lend them such dangerous clothes?"
The old monk said: "I didn't expect them to be so careless! I just wanted them to experience the life of a monk, but I didn't expect them to spend more than half an hour!"
"Then what should we do now?" [[Lei Yangjuan]] asked.
The old monk said: "Now we can only pray that they can change their clothes in time, otherwise there will be no salvation!"
[[Lei Yangjuan]] said: "But how do they know the time? Do they have a watch?"
The old monk said: "No, here are all ancient things, where is there a watch?"
[[Lei Yangjuan]] said: "Then can you remind them?"
The old monk said: "Not really, here are all soundproof walls, where can sound be transmitted?"
[[Lei Yangjuan]] said: "Then can't you go to them?"
The old monk said: "It's not okay, this is a forbidden area, outsiders can't enter!"
[[Lei Yangjuan]] said: "Then what is your use?"
The old monk said: "I... I don't know! I'm just an old monk, what can I do?"
[[Lei Yangjuan]] said: "You can't just give up like this! You have to find a way!"
The old monk said, "Okay, okay, let me think about it..."
Just then, they heard a bell. When the old monk heard it, he was overjoyed and said, "Great! Great! It's the half-hour bell! They should be back!"
[[Lei Yangjuan]] also breathed a sigh of relief, she said: "Really? Really? Take me to see it!"
The old monk said: "Okay, okay, come with me!" He took [[Lei Yangjuan]]'s hand and walked quickly to the backyard.
[[Wang Ximing]] and [[Wang Zhaochu]] also heard the bell, they felt dizzy for a while, and then returned to their original state. They are pleasantly surprised to find themselves back in the present.
[[Wang Ximing]] said: "It's great! It's great! We're finally back!"
[[Wang Zhaochu]] said: "Father, where did we go just now?"
[[Wang Ximing]] said: "We went to the next half hour just now! Do you know that there are many strange things in the next half hour!"
[[Wang Zhaochu]] said: "For example, what?"
[[Wang Ximing]] said: "For example..." He suddenly remembered what happened in the next half hour just now, "For example...it's nothing, it's nothing. Return the clothes to that master."
[[Wang Zhaochu]] said: "Okay."
[[Wang Ximing]] and [[Wang Zhaochu]] walked up to the old monk and returned the clothes to him. The old monk was also very happy to see that they were safe and sound.
The old monk said: "You are back! Great! Great!"
[[Wang Ximing]] said: "Master, thank you for lending us this dress, allowing us to experience a different trip."
The old monk said, "You're welcome, you're welcome. Where did you go after you put on this dress?"
[[Wang Ximing]] said: "We went to the future for half an hour."
The old monk said, "Oh? Is there anything special in the next half hour?"
[[Wang Ximing]] said: "Yes, yes. In the next half hour..." He remembered what happened in the next half hour just now, "The next half hour...in fact, there is nothing special La."
The old monk said, "Really? That's a pity."
At this moment, [[Lei Yangjuan]] followed the old monk to the backyard. As soon as she saw [[Wang Ximing]] and [[Wang Zhaochu]], she ran over excitedly and hugged them.
[[Lei Yangjuan]] said: "Honey! Baby! You are finally back! I am so worried about you!"
[[Wang Ximing]] said: "Honey, I'm sorry for making you worry. We're fine."
[[Wang Zhaochu]] said: "Mom, we just went to a very magical place."
[[Lei Yangjuan]] asked: "Where?"
[[Wang Zhaochu]] said: "We went..." He looked at his father, "We went...to the temple."
[[Lei Yangjuan]] said: "In the temple? Aren't you always in the temple?"
[[Wang Ximing]] said: "Yes, yes. We are in the temple."
[[Lei Yangjuan]] said: "Then where did you go in the temple?"
[[Wang Ximing]] said: "We went..." He looked at the old monk, "We went... to the master's room."
[[Lei Yangjuan]] said: "Master's room? Is there anything interesting about that?"
[[Wang Ximing]] said: "Yes, yes. In the master's room..." He remembered what happened in the master's room just now, "There is actually nothing interesting in the master's room."
[[Lei Yangjuan]] said: "Really? That's really boring."
The old monk felt very uncomfortable when he heard these words. He felt wronged. He wanted to explain, but he was afraid of revealing the secret.
The old monk said: "Uh...Actually...in my room..."
Just then they heard another chime. When the old monk heard it, he was shocked and said: "It's bad! It's bad! It's the hour bell! I forgot to change my clothes!"
[[Lei Yangjuan]] asked: "Change clothes? What change clothes?"
The old monk said: "I am wearing this dress too! It can let me go back to the past or the future for an hour! I just went back to the past for an hour and chatted with my master! I wanted to come back and change clothes, but I forgot the time! It's over an hour now! I'm going to stay in the past hour forever!"
[[Lei Yangjuan]] asked: "What? You are also wearing this dress? It can take you back to the past or the future for an hour? You just went back to the past for an hour to chat with your master?"

'''Guo Jingxing''' (Chinese: ; pinyin: Gu Jngxng; born September 1999) is a Chinese radio host, YouTube uploader and operator. He is one of the co-founders of [[Jiaxing Radio Station]], a popular online radio station that broadcasts music, news, entertainment and culture programs.
== Biography == Guo was born in Hengyang, Hunan province, China. He showed an interest in radio broadcasting since he was young. He passed the independent enrollment exam and entered Hengyang No. 8 Middle School in March 2013. He then passed the college entrance exam and enrolled in Huazhong University of Science and Technology in 2016.
In 2017, he met Liu Jiaxing, a fellow student who shared his passion for radio broadcasting. They decided to start their own online radio station with their own equipment and software. They named it Jiaxing Radio Station after their surnames (Jia from Liu Jiaxing and Xing from Guo Jingxing). They invited some other students to join them as hosts, producers and editors.
Jiaxing Radio Station soon gained popularity among netizens for its diverse and high-quality content. It covers topics such as music, news, entertainment, culture, education, sports and more. It also features interviews with celebrities, experts and ordinary people who have interesting stories to share.
Guo is mainly responsible for uploading and operating the YouTube channel of Jiaxing Radio Station. He also hosts some programs such as "Music Time with Guo Jingxing" and "Guo Jingxing's Movie Reviews". He has a cheerful personality and a good sense of humor. He often interacts with fans on social media platforms such as Weibo, WeChat and Instagram.
Guo has won several awards for his work as a radio host and YouTube uploader. In 2018, he won the Best Newcomer Award at the China Internet Radio Awards. In 2019, he won the Best Host Award at the same event. In 2020, he was nominated for the Best YouTube Channel Award at the China Internet Video Awards.

'''Wang Wuhong'''(Chinese name: '''''', born on {{Birthdate|1965-06-04}}) is the father of [[Wang Ximing]] and the grandfather of [[Wang Zhaochu]]. Wang Wuhong's name was derived from his birthdate coinciding with the [[Wikipedia:Dragon Boat Festival|''Dragon Boat Festival'']], also known as ''Duanwu Festival'', which falls on the fifth day of the fifth lunar month in the Chinese calendar. He currently works at '''River Chief Office in People's Government of Taihetang Town, [[Qidong County]]''', serving as the leader of the water conservancy group of Taihetang Town Agricultural Comprehensive Service Center.[[:File:.pdf|Qidong County Flood Control and Drought Relief Headquarters Document: Notice on Clarifying the Person Responsible for Flood Control and Drought Relief in Our County]] == Experience == In February 2015, participated in the wedding of [[Wang Ximing]] and [[Lei Yangjuan]], and gave a speech as Wang Ximing's father.[[Wang Ximing and Lei Yangjuan's wedding]], https://youtu.be/0wR4AtFiyG0 In 2022, Wang Wuhong was recognized for his outstanding personal achievements in his work at the River Chief Office of Taihetang Town. He has contributed significantly to the implementation of the river chief system, especially in securing funding from the County Agriculture Development Bureau to build a floodgate to address the problem of high water resistance caused by the dam in Luokou Township and the difficult problem of the collapsed river embankment in Shuangpai Village, Caojiaci. From February 2023, he will serve as a correspondent of the Rong Media Center in Qidong County, mainly responsible for reporting on the cleaning of the river, dredging and other work in Taihetang Town, and publicizing the effectiveness, experience, and implementation of the river chief system.http://www.qdxw.com.cn/content/646746/91/12301232.html ==References== [[Category:Biography]] [[Category:Wang Ximing]] [[Category:Wang Zhaochu]] [[Category:People]] [[Category:NoCopy]] [[Category:Wang Wuhong]] {{Navbox_Total}} {{PersonalInfoProtection}}

page.title: Wang and Guo's Beijing Travel Plan in 2017

revision.text:
'''''Wang & Guo Beijing Travel Plan''''' is a Beijing travel plan made by [[Wang Jiaming]] and [[Guo Jingxing]] on June 23, 2017. The plan covers most of the city's famous scenic spots and museums, including the Forbidden City, the Summer Palace, Tiananmen Square, the Temple of Heaven Park, the National Center for the Performing Arts and Nanluoguxiang. Prices and opening hours of each attraction are also listed. Travel time is 710 days. ==Plan summary== This paper introduces three kinds of sightseeing routes in Beijing with different plans. Plan one suggests tourists start at Tiananmen Square and travel west along Chang 'an Avenue, passing scenic spots such as the Great Hall of the People, CCTV and the Summer Palace. The second proposal is to start from Beijing West Railway Station and pass several museums, parks, universities, historical sites and cultural attractions, including the Old Summer Palace, the Summer Palace, Tiananmen Square and the Forbidden City. Plan 3 suggests arriving at Nanyuan Airport first, and then starting from Beijing West Railway Station. The tour route is the same as Plan 2. The attractions include the Museum of Natural History, Peking University, the Temple of Heaven Park, the Ming Tombs and the Badaling Great Wall.
Before departure, you need to prepare necessary items, such as mobile phone, ID card, power bank, etc. In downtown Beijing, you can choose ofo shared bikes or subways and buses to travel to tourist attractions. ==Specific itinerary== On the schedule, the first day can be spent in Lianhua Chi Park, the Capital Museum, the China Century Monument and Yuyuantan Park, followed by visits to the CCTV Tower and the Beijing Planetarium.
The next day itinerary includes: visit Beijing Zoo in the morning, then go to Beijing Exhibition Hall to take photos and have a meal, in the afternoon start to Beijing North Railway Station to take photos, then go to Xueyuan Road to visit the front of various schools to take photos, and finally take a walk in Tsinghua University and find a hotel to rest. The universities visited included Beijing University of Posts and Telecommunications, China University of Political Science and Law, Beijing Film Academy, Beijing University of Aeronautics and Astronautics, Peking University Health Science Center, China University of Geosciences, Beijing University of Science and Technology, and China University of Mining and Technology.
On the morning of the third day, start from the hotel around Tsinghua University and tour Tsinghua University and Peking University by bike. In Tsinghua University, visit the lotus pond, water and wood Tsinghua, I-Zi Hall, the Second School Gate, Tsinghua School and the auditorium. Among them, there are Zhu Ziqing statue, Wen Yiduo statue, Ziqing Pavilion and Wen Pavilion in Shuimu Tsinghua University, and Han Pavilion in recent Spring Garden (in memory of Wu Han). At Peking University, visit the Old School Gate, Weiming Lake, Lake Center Island, Marble Boat, Peking University Red Tower, Bell Pavilion and bronze statue of CAI Yuanpei. It is recommended to buy a map of Tsinghua.
In the afternoon of the third day, we visited the Summer Palace and the Old Summer Palace. It takes a lot of time to visit both sites, so it's important to have plenty of food and water. In the evening, I went to the Olympic Park and visited the Bird's Nest and the Water Cube.
On the morning of Day 4, after visiting the Olympic Park, visit Beihai Park, Jingshan Park, Shichahai Park and the surrounding old hutongs. Eat at Nan Luogu Lane in the evening and then return to the hotel. It is worth mentioning that these parks and attractions have different ticket prices, which requires planning in advance.
In the morning to the Tiananmen Rostrum, and then into the palace browse for more than two hours, the main route for the Meridian Gate, Taihe Gate, Hongyi Pavilion, Hall of Supreme Harmony, Hall of harmony, Hall of preserving harmony, dry Qing Gate, dry Qing Palace, Temple of Communication, Palace of Earthly Tranquility and the imperial garden. Then back to Tiananmen Square, visit the Monument to the People's Heroes, the Great Hall of the People, the National Center for the Performing Arts and the National Museum of China.
In the afternoon, we will go to CCTV, pass Deyunshe, and continue to visit the Temple of Heaven. The tour time is 2 hours. Note that this one day tour may need to be split into two days, the tour time depends on the situation.
The sixth (or seventh) day includes a visit to the Ming Tombs and the Badaling Great Wall. From the Temple of Heaven in the morning, you need to make several transfers to reach your destination. Admission to the Ming Tombs is 135 yuan in high season and 100 yuan in low season, half price for students, and the tour lasts for two hours. After lunch, head to the Badaling Great Wall. Admission is 45 yuan for adults and 22.5 yuan for students. After spending 34 hours on the Great Wall, return to Beijing West Railway Station in the afternoon. ==References== [[:File:.pdf|Beijing Travel Plan.pdf]] [[zh:(2017)]] {{Navbox_Total}}

<div class="nocopy">[[zh:]] Zuo Jun and Wang Ting held their wedding at [[Qidong]] Yizhou Hotel on August 25, 2019. The organizers of this wedding are [[Qidong]] Zhimei Wedding and [[Qidong]] Yizhou Hotel, and the film and television production is in charge of CC Yinghua Wedding. The entire wedding host team is from the Hunan Forerunner host team, and the wedding host is Meng Fei.
The two have known each other and fell in love for nearly two years. From the initial heartbeat to the final firm choice, being with each other has become their longest confession of love. In daily life, Zuo Jun gives people the impression of being shy and restrained. Therefore, this wedding can be said to be the most romantic moment he planned for Wang Ting, and it also met the bride's innermost expectations.
